data.description: Welcome Home, This recently remodeled and updated home is waiting for it's new family. This home is conveniently located to downtown Pensacola, NAS and so much more. The granite countertops and stainless appliances make this kitchen a wonderful work space and the open spaces give the illusion of much more room. Call today and take a look!
